      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/netanyahu-withdraws-ex-admiral-s-nomination-as-shin-bet-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本杰明·内塔尼亚胡（Benjamin Netanyahu）在宣布后24小时后，撤回了他提名的，他提名为申贝特安全部门的董事。]]></description>
