      <title>莫桑比克审查石油和天然气法以提高当地利益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/mozambique-starts-review-of-mining-oil-and-gas-laws</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克已经开始了一个过程，以审查和现代化东南非洲国家的采矿，石油和天然气的法律框架，以提高当地利益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/mozambique-starts-review-of-mining-oil-and-gas-laws</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 18:23:08 GMT</pubDate>
